[thinking] **Examining installation issues**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering the use of `BlockHound.install()`, but it may not work well with Native Image because of unsupported features. The preflight indicates it should be installed just once. I think the active `NexusAccessor` will come into play during the instrumentation, especially when transformed classes are loading their type initializers. Hm, maybe using the ByteBuddy API directly might simplify things. I should take a closer look at the existing tests to see what they reveal.
[thinking] 
